import React from "react"; import Title from "../layouts/Title"; import { projectOne, projectTwo, projectThree, projectFour, projectFive, projectSix, projectSeven, } from "../../assets/index"; import ProjectsCard from "./ProjectsCard"; const Projects = () => { return (
</div> <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-6 xl:gap-14"> <ProjectsCard title="Live File Sharing App" des="A real-time file-sharing application with authentication, file previews, and cloud storage." src={projectOne} githubLink="https://github.com/yourusername/live-file-sharing" liveLink="https://liveshare.kesug.com" /> <ProjectsCard title="E-commerce Website" des="A full-stack e-commerce platform with user authentication, payment integration, and a modern UI." src={projectTwo} githubLink="https://github.com/yourusername/ecommerce" liveLink="https://your-ecommerce-site.com" /> <ProjectsCard title="Chatting App" des="A real-time chat application with group chat, media sharing, and push notifications." src={projectThree} githubLink="https://github.com/Smegne/react-chatap" liveLink="https://yourchatapp.com" /> <ProjectsCard title="Booking System" des="An online booking system with scheduling, payments, and user dashboard features." src={projectFour} githubLink="https://github.com/yourusername/booking-app" liveLink="https://yourbookingapp.com" /> <ProjectsCard title="Amazon E-commerce Clone" des="A full-stack Amazon clone with product search, user authentication, and checkout functionality." src={projectFive} githubLink="https://github.com/yourusername/amazon-clone" liveLink="https://youramazonclone.com" /> <ProjectsCard title="Zoom Clone" des="A video conferencing app with screen sharing, chat, and meeting scheduling features." src={projectSix} githubLink="https://github.com/yourusername/zoom-clone" liveLink="https://yourzoomclone.com" /> <ProjectsCard title="Evangai Network Clone" des="A social media network clone with profile customization, posts, and real-time messaging." src={projectSeven} githubLink="https://github.com/yourusername/evangai-clone" liveLink="https://yourevangaiclone.com" /> </div> </section> ); }; export default Projects;
